::Striker::

Striker looks at Spears as she offers him company. He was used to training 
alone, but company might be welcome. "I ussually train solo, but company 
wouldn't hurt, I guess."

"Power recharged. Ready for takeoff."

He turns his head to look at the computer as it reports that, standing up. 
"Allright, let's fly."

He presses a few buttons on the console, the pod taking off again.
